    seo_description: 'Discover how to wear a three-piece suit with confidence. Waistcoat styling tips, occasion guidance and outfit ideas from William Ashford\'s British tailoring experts.',
    intro_text: 'The three-piece suit is a statement of sartorial commitment — a garment that speaks of tradition, craftsmanship, and considered dressing. Adding a waistcoat to your suit transforms the silhouette and creates a layered formality that the two-piece simply cannot achieve. At William Ashford, the three-piece suit sits at the heart of our collection, worn by men who understand that dressing well is both an art and a discipline.',
